\c 26
\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngeTire
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wetshumi lanye, ngolokuqala lwenyanga, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi, lisithi:
\v 2 Ndodana yomuntu, ngenxa yokuthi iTire itshilo ngeJerusalema\x + Isa. 23.1.\x* \add isithi\add*: Aha, yephukile ebingamasango abantu; isiphendukele kimi; ngizagcwaliswa, ichithekile\x + 25.3. 33.21.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngimelane lawe, wena Tire, ngenze izizwe ezinengi zenyuke zimelane lawe\x + Jer. 34.1.\x*, njengolwandle lusenza amagagasi alo enyuke\x + Lilo 2.13.\x*.
\v 4 Njalo zizachitha imiduli yeTire, zibhidlizele phansi imiphotshongo yayo; ngiphale inhlabathi yayo kuyo, ngiyenze\x + 26.14.\x* ibe lidwala elize\x + 24.7.\x*.
\v 5 Izakuba yindawo yokuchayela amambule\x + 26.14. 32.3. 47.10.\x*, phakathi kolwandle\x + 27.32.\x*; ngoba mina ngikhulumile, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 21.17.\x*; njalo izakuba yimpango yezizwe\x + 7.21.\x*.
\v 6 Lamadodakazi ayo asensimini azabulawa ngenkemba\x + 26.8. 16.27.\x*. Njalo bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.7.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 7 Ngoba itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngizaletha phezu kweTire uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 29.18.\x*, inkosi yamakhosi\x + Ezra 7.12. Dan. 2.37. Hos. 8.10.\x*, evela enyakatho, elamabhiza, lezinqola, labagadi bamabhiza, lamaxuku, labantu abanengi\x + Jer. 1.14.\x*.
\v 8 Uzabulala ngenkemba amadodakazi akho ensimini\x + 26.8. 16.27.\x*, enze umduli wokuvimbezela emelene lawe\x + 4.2.\x*, abuthelele idundulu emelene lawe\x + 4.2.\x*\x + 2 Sam. 20.15. Luka 19.43.\x*, aphakamise isihlangu esikhulu simelene lawe\x + 2 Kho. 19.32.\x*.
\v 9 Uzamisa imigqala yokudiliza imelane lemiduli yakho, adilizele phansi imiphotshongo yakho ngezinkemba zakhe.
\v 10 Ngenxa yobunengi bamabhiza akhe uthuli lwawo luzakusibekela; imiduli yakho izanyikinywa ngumsindo wabagadi bamabhiza lamavili lezinqola, nxa ezangena emasangweni akho, njengokungena emzini ofohlelwayo\x + 10.2.\x*.
\v 11 Ngamasondo amabhiza akhe uzanyathela zonke izitalada zakho; uzabulala abantu bakho ngenkemba, lensika zakho eziqinileyo ziwele emhlabathini.
\v 12 Njalo bazaphanga inotho yakho\x + 29.19.\x*, bathumbe\x + 29.19.\x* impahla yakho ethengiswayo\x + 28.5,16,18.\x*, badilizele phansi imiduli yakho, babhidlize izindlu zakho eziloyisekayo, bafake amatshe akho lezigodo zakho lothuli lwakho phakathi kwamanzi\x + 26.4.\x*.
\v 13 Ngizakwenza kuphele umsindo wengoma zakho\x + Isa. 14.11. 24.8. Jer. 7.34.\x*, lelizwi lamachacho akho kalisayikuzwakala\x + 28.13. Isa. 5.12. 23.16.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo ngizakwenza ube lidwala elize\x + 26.14.\x*; uzakuba yindawo yokuchayela amambule\x + 26.14. 32.3. 47.10.\x*, kawusayikwakhiwa; ngoba mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngikhulumile, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 21.17.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova kuyo iTire: Izihlenge kaziyikunyikinyeka yini ngomdumo wokuwa kwakho\x + 26.18. 27.28. 31.16. Jer. 49.21.\x*, lapho abalimeleyo bebubula, lapho kubulawa okubulawayo phakathi kwakho\x + Jer. 51.52.\x*?
\v 16 Khona zonke iziphathamandla zolwandle\x + Isa. 23.8.\x* zizakwehla ezihlalweni zazo zobukhosi\x + Jona 3.6.\x*, zikhulule izigqoko zazo\x + Jona 3.6.\x*, zikhuphe izembatho zazo ezifekethisiweyo\x + 16.10.\x*; zizembathise ukuthuthumela, zihlale emhlabathini\x + Jona 3.6.\x*\x + Isa. 3.26.\x*, zithuthumele\x + 32.10.\x* ngaso \add sonke\add* isikhathi\x + Jobe 7.18.\x*, zimangale kakhulu ngawe\x + 27.35.\x*.
\v 17 Zizakuphakamisela isililo\x + 27.2,32. 19.1. Isam. 18.9.\x*, zithi kuwe: Uchithwe njani ezinlwandle wena owawuhlalwa, umuzi olodumo, owawulamandla olwandle\x + Isa. 23.4.\x*, wona labahlali bawo, abamisa ukwesabeka kwabo kuye wonke umhlali wawo\x + 32.23.\x*!
\v 18 Khathesi izihlenge zizathuthumela\x + 26.15.\x* ngosuku lokuwa kwakho, yebo, izihlenge eziselwandle zizakhathazeka ngokuphuma kwakho\x + 27.27.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Lapho ngizakwenza \add ube\add* ngumuzi olunxiwa, njengemizi engahlalwayo; lapho ngizakwenyusa ukujula phezu kwakho, lamanzi amanengi akusibekele\x + 27.34.\x*;
\v 20 khona ngizakwehlisela phansi lalabo abehlela emgodini\x + 32.18. 31.14.\x*, ebantwini basendulo\x + Jobe 22.15. 2 Pet. 2.5.\x*, ngikuhlalise ezindaweni eziphansi zomhlaba\x + 32.18. 31.14.\x*, emanxiweni asendulo\x + 38.12. Jobe 3.14.\x*, lalabo abehlela emgodini, ukuze ungahlalwa\x + 32.18. 31.14.\x*; njalo ngizabeka udumo elizweni labaphilayo\x + 32.23-27,32. Hlab. 27.13.\x*.
\v 21 Ngizakwenza ube ngokwesabekayo okukhulu\x + 27.36. 28.19. Isam. 18.21.\x*, unga\add sa\add*bikho\x + 27.36. 28.19. Isam. 18.21.\x*; lanxa udingwa\x + Hlab. 37.36.\x*, ungatholakali futhi kuze kube nininini, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + Hlab. 37.36.\x*\x + Dan. 11.19.\x*.
